^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, let us discuss a couple of the bidding aspects. First, should Patti open? Again, if you use traditional methods, it does not meet the rule of 20. But if you use Bergen's methods, she has 11 HCP, 1 length + 1 quality suit, enough to open. So, Marty Bergen, Mr. "Rule of 20" would approve of Patti 's opening bid. |
